(82, 483, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'Elderflower Syrup 750ml', '<em>Floral</em> and <em>sweet</em> in flavour, ODK <strong>elderflower cocktail</strong> syrup can make a great and unique addition to many a creation, be it drink or food. This intensely fragrant and floral syrup not only tastes like the real deal but looks the part too, served in an elegant glass bottle that sits stylishly on your back bar or upon a shelf. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '4.6', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/elderflower-fiori-di-sambuco-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(83, 485, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'Rhubarb Syrup 750ml', 'Tart and <em>slightly sour</em> in flavour, <strong>rhubarb</strong> is a flavour which often finds itself in the culinary world. Exploring the sour notes of ODK rhubarb cocktail syrup can lead to some tasty discoveries, particularly when combined with more exotic ingredients. Served in our stylish glass bottles, allowing you to enjoy not only the taste of ODK rhubarb cocktail syrup but also its vibrant colour as it sits comfortably upon your back bar. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '4.6', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/rhubarb-rabarbaro-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(84, 487, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'Falernum Syrup 750ml', '<strong>Falernum</strong> is a flavour that was coined in the <em>Caribbean</em>. Although it can be made in many ways falernum syrup usually contains flavours of <em>almond</em>, <em>ginger</em>, <em>lime</em> and <em>vanilla</em>, as well as <em>cloves</em> and <em>allspice</em> in some instances. Our own Falernum syrup is as much as mystery as the story behind its invention. Best used in tropical drinks, what you can do with ODK falernum syrup is only limited by your creativity. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '4.6', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/falernum-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(85, 489, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'Violet Syrup 750ml', '<em>Floral</em> and <em>sweet</em> in flavour, ODK <strong>violet cocktail</strong> syrup can make a great and unique addition to many a creation, be it drink or food. This <em>fragrant</em> and <em>floral</em> syrup not only tastes like the real deal but looks the part too, served in an elegant glass bottle that sits stylishly on your back bar or upon a shelf. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '4', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/violet-violetta-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(86, 491, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'Cinnamon Syrup 750ml', 'With an instantly recognisable aroma and taste, ODK <strong>cinnamon</strong> syrup can be a great addition to a whole variety of hot drinks or winter warmer cocktails. One of the few flavours that can make you feel warmer on a cold day, <em>enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '4', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/cinnamon-cannella-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(87, 493, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'Vanilla Syrup 750ml', 'Bring a burst of flavour to your hot drinks with ODK <strong>vanilla</strong> syrup. The <em>floral</em> and <em>woody</em> flavour of <em>vanilla pods</em> have become a staple addition in many a hot drink over the years. What you can achieve with ODK vanilla syrup is limited only by the imagination. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '4', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/vanilla-vaniglia-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(88, 495, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'Caramel Syrup 750ml', '<em>Potent</em> in its taste, ODK <strong>caramel</strong> syrup can be the perfect addition for a <em>touch of sweetness</em> with an element of <em>smooth and subtle</em> flavour. Caramel cocktail syrup is a great way to switch up a latte or creamy coffee, giving it an extra dimension of flavour alongside the deep, aromatic coffee beans. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '4', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/caramel-caramello-1-2.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(89, 497, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'Ginger Syrup 750ml', 'ODK <strong>ginger cocktail</strong> syrup is strong and aromatic. Infused with the complex character of <em>ginger</em>, this syrup infuses elements of <em>spice</em> and <em>zest</em> with <em>sweetness</em> and <em>warmth</em>. With an unmistakable taste and aroma ODK ginger cocktail syrup can be an interesting addition to many a dish or drink. Served in a stylish glass bottle, this ODK syrup was designed to be showed off. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '4', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/ginger-zenzero-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(90, 499, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'Orgeat Syrup 750ml', '<strong>Orgeat</strong> syrup is a longstanding flavour in the cocktail world. Made form a combination of <em>almonds</em>, <em>sugar</em> and <em>rose water</em>, ODK orgeat cocktail syrup has a pronounced almond taste and can be used for a variety of flavouring situations be it cocktails, hot drinks or in the preparation of food. What you can achieve with ODK syrup is limited only by the imagination. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '4', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/orgeat-orzata-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(91, 501, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'White Mint Syrup 750ml', '<em>Mint</em> is an unmistakably <em>fresh</em> and <em>potent</em> flavour. It is advisable to use this flavour in moderation, as the fragrant and unique flavour of mint can easily dominate. A perfect replacement for the real thing in the most famous mint-based cocktail of all time, the mojito, a touch of this ODK syrup is all you will need. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '4', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/white-mint-menta-bianca-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(92, 503, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'Coconut Syrup 750ml', 'Bring a burst of flavour to your food and drink with ODK <strong>coconut cocktail</strong> syrup. The unique and distinctive taste of <em>coconut</em> has become a staple flavour in many a Tiki cocktail over the years and matches perfectly with other exotic fruits. What you can achieve with ODK syrup is limited only by the imagination. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>\r<br>\r<br><strong>Application</strong>\r<br><ul>\r<br>	<li>Cocktails</li>\r<br>	<li>Mocktails</li>\r<br>	<li>Milkshakes</li>\r<br>	<li>Smoothies</li>\r<br>	<li>Latte</li>\r<br>	<li>Coffee based</li>\r<br>	<li>Lemonades</li>\r<br></ul>\r<br><strong>Pack</strong>\r<br>\r<br>750 ml bottle', '', 1, '', '4', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/coconut-cocco-1-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(93, 505, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'Tropical Blu Syrup 750ml', 'Renowned for its <em>deep blue colour</em>, ODK <strong>tropical blue cocktail</strong> syrup combines the <em>fruity flavours</em> of many different fruits resulting in a <em>tropical</em> and <em>citrusy</em> syrup. Similar to ODK grenadine cocktail syrup, a dash of tropical blue syrup can make a great addition to a variety of food and drinks if only for its vibrant colour. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '4', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/tropical-blu-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(94, 507, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'Grenadine Syrup 750ml', 'Otherwise known as pomegranate syrup, <strong>grenadine cocktail</strong> syrup has been a consistent addition to cocktails and mocktails alike for a long time. <em>Intensely sweet</em> and <em>deep red</em> in colour ODK grenadine cocktail syrup is the perfect addition to a whole range of summer drinks. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '4', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/grenadine-granatina-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(95, 509, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'Strawberry Syrup 750ml', 'Bring a burst of flavour to your food and drink with ODK <strong>strawberry cocktail</strong> syrup. The <em>mouth-watering</em> taste of <em>sweet strawberries</em> has become a staple flavour in many a cocktail over the years. What you can achieve with ODK syrup is limited only by the imagination. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '4', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/strawberry-fragola-1-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(96, 511, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'Brown Sugar 750ml', '<strong>Brown sugar</strong> syrup is a staple in the world of cocktails and coffees. The perfect sweetener, ODK brown sugar syrup is the perfect aid to balance out your flavour profile. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '4', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/brown-sugar-zucchero-di-canna-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
