(109, 540, '', 206, 'Syrups', 'Bubble Gum Syrup 750ml', '<strong>Bubblegum</strong> is a distinctive flavour, immediately recognisable for its sweet and fruity taste. Often made up of a mixture of <em>banana</em>, <em>cherry</em> and <em>strawberry</em>, the bubblegum flavour can make a great and unique addition to many a creation, be it a cocktail, hot drink or even flavoured gelato. ODK bubblegum cocktail syrup not only tastes like the real deal but looks the part too, served in an elegant glass bottle that sits stylishly on your back bar or upon a shelf. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '4.6', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bubblegum-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(110, 542, '', 210, 'Syrups', 'Creamy White Chocolate', 'Combining an unbeatable taste with unmissable bottle, ODK <strong>white chocolate</strong> is as good as it looks. Laced with the <em>sweetness</em> of <em>white chocolate</em> to ensure the flavour is well balanced, this cream will layer perfectly on top of your hot drinks. Effortless coffee art is just around the corner with ODK creams. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>\r<br>\r<br><strong>Application</strong>\r<br><ul>\r<br>	<li>Latte art</li>\r<br>	<li>Coffee based drinks</li>\r<br>	<li>Milkshakes</li>\r<br>	<li>Cocktails</li>\r<br>	<li>Mocktails</li>\r<br></ul>\r<br><strong>Pack</strong>\r<br>\r<br>750 ml bottles • 6 bottles/box', '', 1, '', '6.9', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/white-chocolate-cioccolato-bianco-1.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(111, 544, '', 209, 'Syrups', 'Coffee Kick', 'For the ultimate lover of coffee, ODK <strong>coffee kick frappe</strong> powder combines coffee flavour with coffee. What more could you want? The result is a frappe that will leave you wanting more. Mix with ice and whipped cream, sit back, relax and cool down on a hot day. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '7.5', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Coffee-Kick.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(112, 547, '', 209, 'Syrups', 'Frozen Mocha', 'For a hit of coffee and chocolate all mixed into one perfectly balanced ice-cold drink, ODK frozen mocha is what you need. Bursting with the bitterness of the coffee beans and balanced with the smooth, sweetness of the chocolate this frappe is a bit of a flavour sensation. <em>Enjoy drinks the right way, enjoy ODK.</em>', '', 1, '', '7.5', 'ODK', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Frozen-Mocha.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
