(119, 775, '', 109, 'Machine', 'NEW! For Pre-Order: Saeco Area for Lavazza BLUE Capsules (*FREE Milk Chiller for a Limited Time!)', '[embed]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WK1YGKsP7xI&feature=youtu.be[/embed]\r<br>\r<br><strong>Will reach Bahrain in a month from the time we receive your online order.</strong>\r<br>\r<br>*Packaged Fresh Milk Chiller is sold separately for BD 150\r<br>\r<br>A SIMPLE TOUCH. Area OTC HSC, the evolution of perfection.\r<br>\r<br>Thanks to the Saeco One Touch Cappuccino system, and to the double boiler for the High-Speed Cappuccino function, you can get a top-quality cappuccino quickly with just one touch.\r<br>\r<br>The tested “Pinless Wonder” system makes it possible to brew a consistently excellent hot drink, one cup after the other for users to enjoy\r<br>\r<br>The practical system allows adjusting the height of the dispenser at three different levels making it possible to use all kinds of cups and to be very versatile.', 'Italian design is recognized throughout the world for its creativity and rationality.\r<br>\r<br>Area is 100% made in Italy, the result of Saeco’s constant efforts to attain increasingly high standards.\r<br>\r<br>The measured lines and the style of its finishing are clear even in the smallest details.\r<br>\r<br>Its chrome finish, the high quality of its materials, the wide and modern user interface with its easy-to-use icons and display are the result of years of experience in the field of professional coffee machines.\r<br>\r<br>Thanks to the backlit icons that ensure an intuitive use of the machine, it is possible to brew up to 8 different direct selection beverages easily.\r<br>\r<br>Simplicity and performance, for a top-quality product always', 1, '500', '550', 'Saeco', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Area1.jpg, https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Area3.jpg, https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Area2.jpg, https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Milk-C