(120, 564, '', 109, 'Machine', 'Saeco Aulika with Packaged Dometic Fresh Milk Chiller', 'Aulika is the perfect combination of aesthetics and professional performance. It has a clean, rational design and unparalleled technology: double hydraulic circuit, conical blades, and large water and coffee capacity (for the Aulika Top and Mid models). All these characteristics make this machine perfect for locations with high daily consumptions.', '', 1, '', '1200', 'Saeco', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Saeco-Aulika-2.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(121, 559, '', 109, 'Machine', 'Saeco Lirika OTC with Packaged Dometic Fresh Milk Chiller', 'OTC (One Touch Cappuccino) is the top version of Saeco Lirika automatic coffee machines. With the OTC system you can brew a cappuccino or latte macchiato with a click of a button!\r<br>\r<br>Lirika is a simple, compact and performing automatic coffee machine, ideal for the office and small Ho.Re.Ca. venues. It has modern and essential lines, high capacity water and coffee tanks and is incredibly easy to use.\r<br>\r<br>Cappuccino and latte macchiato shall be especially easy to prepare with this machine, with its “<strong>One Touch Cappuccino</strong>” system.\r<br>\r<br>Indeed, thanks to the new and innovative “Pinless Wonder” cappuccinatore, created in the Philips research laboratories and applied to the Saeco products, it is possible to obtain fresh milk-based drinks of the<strong> highest quality and taste</strong>, in the best Italian tradition.', '', 1, '680', '800', 'Saeco', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Saeco-Lirika-OTC.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(122, 797, '', 109, 'Machine', 'Saeco Phedra Evo Automatic Bean-To-Cup Espresso Machine with Automatic  Cappuccinatore', '[embed]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZcPGbNLk2nc&feature=emb_logo[/embed]\r<br><h2 class=\"titolobloccodue\">Minimal design\r<br>for your space.</h2>\r<br><p class=\"txtdue\">The new, refined, minimalist design stands out for its interface. The icons, backlit touch buttons and generously sized colour display provide an instant readout of the available options and facilitate your choice.</p>\r<br>Phedra Evo is ideal for elegant environments frequented by an average number of people, such as offices, meeting rooms, lobby or hotel breakfast rooms. Although it is small in size, Phedra Evo is the ideal table-top coffee machine since it is able to provide a broad range of beverages based on coffee, milk and chocolate besides hot water for tea and herbal infusions.', 'Ideal for Coffee Shops, Hotels, Restaurants, even in workplaces.\r<br>\r<br>&nbsp;', 1, '', '1550', 'Saeco', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Phedra-Evo-Cappuccino-4.jpg, https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Phedra-Evo-Cappuccino-1.jpg, https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Phedra-Evo-Cappuccino-3.jpg, https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Phedra-Evo-Cappuccino-2.jpg, https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Milk-Chiller-1.jpg, https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Turkish-Coffee-Machine-3.jpg, https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/21-Mixed-Capsule-Turkish-Coffee.png', 0, '1', 0),
(123, 820, '', 106, 'Machine', 'Wega Pegaso 2-Group Professional Espresso Machine', 'Automatic with volumetric dosage espresso coffee machine and high cup group - 122mm\r<br><div>Electronic coffee machine with 4 programmable doses per group. Two steam wands and automatic hot water outlet. Built-in motor and pump.</div>\r<br><div></div>\r<br><div></div>\r<br><div>Call us or better yet, visit our showroom to discuss our special package for your business.</div>', '', 1, '', '3000', 'Wega', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Wega-Pegaso-1.jpg, https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Wega-Pegaso-2.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
(124, 731, '', 106, 'Machine', 'Wega Wbar', '<div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-4 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-one fusion-border-below-title\">\r<br><h1 class=\"title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" data-fontsize=\"50\" data-lineheight=\"70px\">A rational design for an intuitive experience.</h1>\r<br></div>\r<br><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-6 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-four fusion-border-below-title\">\r<br><h4 class=\"title-heading-left fusion-responsive-typography-calculated\" data-fontsize=\"18\" data-lineheight=\"27px\"><strong>Design</strong></h4>\r<br></div>\r<br><div class=\"fusion-text\">\r<br><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">“The design is conceived by revising the shapes of traditional coffee machines, which reduces the overall dimensions and enhances the two groups with the control systems.</span></p>\r<br>Practical and intuitive. The new WBar steam lever is based on\r<br>these two principles, allowing the barista to work quickly and\r<br>smoothly. There are two different ways to steam: continuous flow or on\r<br>demand. The screenprinted steam handle makes for an even more intuitive\r<br>way of working, as well as providing a distinctive design feature.\r<br>\r<br>The cylindrical groups, with their distinctive anodised orange\r<br>colour, house the vertically-arranged control consoles.\r<br>Each button panel is back-lit and offers the option of programming\r<br>up to four doses. The combination of two navigation keys gives access\r<br>to the automatic wash cycle. A spot LED is positioned between\r<br>the groups, creating an elegant strip of light on the work area.\r<br>\r<br>The WBar’s attractive design also includes four function buttons\r<br>positioned on the sides of the groups: two emergency keys,\r<br>a cupwarmer button, if present, and a hot water dispensing button for\r<br>making tea.”\r<br>\r<br></div>', 'Advance order: Will reach Bahrain in 30 to 45 days', 1, '3800', '4500', 'Wega', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/wega1.jpg, https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/sr-attachment-icon-360_one.png', 0, '1', 0),
