(126, 573, '', 110, 'Lavazza Products > Coffee Accessories', 'Milkeasy - Lavazza Cappuccino Maker', 'MilkEasy The new frother that whisks milk to perfection. A few simple steps to prepare lots of delicious hot and cold milk-based recipes in your own home. MILK FROTHERS Features Technical Data Sheets Milkeasy Create your cappuccino Thanks to MilkEasy, you can prepare the authentic Italian cappuccino with a creamy and velvety foam at home, and not only that: with a touch of the button you can warm or froth the milk to create many original recipes based on milk, hot and cold. Design and simplicity The ultimate in practicality and elegance. With MilkEasy, you can bring a touch of modern elegance to your kitchen. It is so small that it fits in every space and is incredibly easy to use.\r<br><ul>\r<br>	<li>The Milk Easy will beep twice to tell you it’s finished.</li>\r<br>	<li>Maximum capacity for milk frothing 120 (internal level indicator: foam) ml</li>\r<br>	<li>Maximum capacity for milk heating 180 (internal level indicator: milk) ml</li>\r<br>	<li>Removable parts (cover, seal, whisk) are dishwasher safe</li>\r<br>	<li>Dimension: 230 mm(H) x 130 mm(D) x 205 mm(W)</li>\r<br></ul>', '', 1, '', '28', 'Lavazza', 'https://ilmercatobh.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/MilkEasy-Both.jpg', 0, '1', 0),
